OL,3,CPlymouth teen praises hospital staff
OL,4,Cafter 'nightmare' IT failure
OL,6,FToby Dixon told ITV News' Sam
OL,7,FBlackledge about his experience at
OL,8,FDerriford Hospital.
OL,10,FA teenager from Plymouth who was
OL,11,Fadmitted to Derriford Hospital's
OL,12,Femergency department during a recent
OL,13,Fmajor IT failure has praised staff for
OL,14,Fdoing their best to cope.
OL,16,FToby Dixon says his 'eye-opening'
OL,17,Fexperience showed how the city's
OL,18,Fhealthcare system is struggling to
OL,19,Fkeep up.
