OL,3,CPlymouth teen praises hospital staff
OL,4,Cafter 'nightmare' IT failure
OL,6,FHis mum Sara said something needs to
OL,7,Fchange, or things will get worse.
OL,9,FToby, 18, was admitted to the hospital
OL,10,Fon 4 April this year and said IT
OL,11,Fissues were impacting on some key
OL,12,Fclinical systems.
OL,14,FSara said she was shocked by what she
OL,15,Fsaw.
OL,17,F"The queue was out the door, between
OL,18,F70 and 100 people. There was a two
OL,19,Fhour and 40 minute wait for triage,
OL,20,Fand nearly a nine-hour wait just to
OL,21,Fsee a doctor.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
