OL,3,CPlymouth teen praises hospital staff
OL,4,Cafter 'nightmare' IT failure
OL,6,F"I was gobsmacked. It was 8.30pm and
OL,7,Fto think that we were maybe not going
OL,8,Fto see a doctor until the morning....I
OL,9,Fwas thinking please God, let's pray
OL,10,Fthat we get seen a bit sooner."
OL,12,FToby said staff were "doing the best
OL,13,Fthey could" in the circumstances,
OL,14,Fresorting to using whiteboards and
OL,15,Fpaper and pens instead of computers.
