OL,3,CPlymouth teen praises hospital staff
OL,4,Cafter 'nightmare' IT failure
OL,6,FChief nurse Darryn Allcorn said: "We
OL,7,Fhave a lot of electronic systems, so
OL,8,Fat any given time we know exactly
OL,9,Fwhere people are in the building
OL,10,Fdigitally, we can visualise wards, we
OL,11,Fcan visualise the emergency department.
OL,13,F"When we lose our IT, we then have to
OL,14,Fgo on to paper systems. So while we
OL,15,Fcan maintain patient safety,
OL,16,Fcommunication across the hospital
OL,17,Ftakes much more time."
