OL,3,CPlymouth teen praises hospital staff
OL,4,Cafter 'nightmare' IT failure
OL,6,FChief operating officer Jo Beer said:
OL,7,F"There is no easy answer. ED is full.
OL,8,FIt's crowded. It is a poor experience
OL,9,Ffor patients.
OL,11,F"They are waiting too long to get into
OL,12,Fthe department or too long to move
OL,13,Finto a bed in the hospital, and that
OL,14,Fcan't be a great experience.
