OL,3,CPlymouth teen praises hospital staff
OL,4,Cafter 'nightmare' IT failure
OL,6,F"Some of our challenges are the
OL,7,Fmismatch between the number of people
OL,8,Fwaiting to get into the hospital -
OL,9,Feither for emergency care or for
OL,10,Fserious planned surgery or
OL,11,Finvestigations - on balance with the
OL,12,Fpeople who are leaving hospital and
OL,13,Ffit to go home.
OL,15,F"It's the time of year where we see a
OL,16,Freduction in demand, a reduction in
OL,17,Fpressures, and we've felt that for two
OL,18,Fweeks, and that has meant we've had a
OL,19,Flower level of occupancy.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/7
