OL,3,CPlymouth teen praises hospital staff
OL,4,Cafter 'nightmare' IT failure
OL,6,F"We've worked at such a high level of
OL,7,Fpressure for so long that we've
OL,8,Fslickened a lot of our processes."
OL,10,FWithin the next two weeks a new ward
OL,11,Fwill open with 23 beds in it, and a
OL,12,Fnew urgent treatment centre will take
OL,13,Fsome pressure off the emergency
OL,14,Fdepartment.
